title: Blue Moon of Kentucky
lyrics:
Blue moon of Kentucky, keep on shining
Shine on the one that's gone and left me blue
Blue moon of Kentucky, keep on shining
Shine on the one that's gone and left me blue
It was on one moonlight night
Stars shining bright

Whisper on high

Love said goodbye

Blue moon of Kentucky keep on shining

Shine on the one that's gone and left me blue
